OL,5, Adults should stop mocking young people
OL,6, by calling them "woke" for standing up 
OL,7, for things they believe in, says a     
OL,8, leading head teacher.                  
OL,10,FSamantha Price, president of the Girls'
OL,11,FSchools Association, is urging parents 
OL,12,Fand teachers to keep up with the       
OL,13,Fyounger generation instead.            
OL,15,FShe will tell a conference on Monday   
OL,16,Fthat pupils are genuinely worried about
OL,17,Fracism, sexism and climate change.     
OL,19,FThey want to address these issues with 
OL,20,Fsupport from adults, she adds.         
